

Gema Mode activatability:


| Description                       | Expected result           |
|-----------------------------------|---------------------------|
| Load non gema map in non ctf mode | Gema mode not activatable |
| Load gema map in non ctf mode     | Gema mode not activatable |
| View demo of gema map in ctf mode | Gema mode not activatable |
| Load gema map in ctf mode         | Gema mode activatable     |


Auto activate gema mode:

| Description                       | Expected result           |
|-----------------------------------|---------------------------|
| Load non gema map in non ctf mode | Gema mode not activating  |
| Load gema map in non ctf mode     | Gema mode not activating  |
| View demo of gema map in ctf mode | Gema mode not activating  |
| Load gema map in ctf mode         | Gema mode activating      |
